busdesc: As of September 17, 2019, Total System Services, Inc. was acquired by Global Payments Inc. Total System Services, Inc. provides payment processing, merchant, and related payment services to financial and nonfinancial institutions worldwide.

Synovus Financial Corp. operates as the bank holding company for Synovus Bank that provides various financial products and services. It operates through three segments: Community Banking, Wholesale Banking, and Financial Management Services.
Snap-on Incorporated manufactures and markets tools, equipment, diagnostics, and repair information and systems solutions for professional users worldwide.
Meredith Corporation operates as a diversified media company primarily in the United States. It operates in two segments, National Media and Local Media.
